<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/graham-razey> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Graham Razey was appointed Deputy Further Education (FE) Commissioner in December 2025. He has worked in the education sector for over 31 years, including as Chief Executive of East Kent College Group for 15 years. Graham also has previous experience as a: National Leader of Further Education member of the Department for Education Principal’s Reference Group chair of a multi-academy trust board member on several education, skills and community organisations"@en .
